主要翻译
 
tropical adj (climate: hot, humid)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带的，热带气候的，潮热的 rè dài de ，rè dài qì hòu de ，cháo rè de TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶的  (气候：热带)
 -- I was extremely glad to be leaving that tropical climate.
 
tropical adj (plant, animal: of the tropics)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带的 rè dài de TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶的  (植物、动物)
 -- We love tropical fruits like mangoes and papayas.

复合形式： 
 
nontropical, non-tropical adj (not tropical)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 非热带的 fēi rè dài de TC Traditional Chinese 非熱帶的  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 不是热带的 fēi rè dài de，bú shì rè dài de 
 
semitropical, semi-tropical adj (geography: subtropical)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 亚热带的 yà rè dài de TC Traditional Chinese 亞熱帶的  (地理术语)
 
tropical aquarium n (tank of tropical fish)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 饲养热带鱼的鱼缸 sì yǎng rè dài yú de yú gāng  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 恒温鱼缸 sì yǎng rè dài yú de yú gāng，héng wēn yú gāng 
 -- This tropical aquarium has angelfish, clown loaches, and other colorful varieties.
 
tropical cyclone n (hurricane with rainstorms)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带气旋 rè dài qì xuán TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶氣旋  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带暴风 rè dài qì xuán，rè dài bào fēng 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 飓风 rè dài qì xuán，jù fēng 
 -- The tropical cyclone caused widespread flooding on the coast.
 
tropical fish n (fish from tropical waters)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带鱼 rè dài yú TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶魚  
 -- Many collectors of tropical fish are particularly proud of their angelfish.
 
tropical forest n (dense woodland in equatorial area)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带雨林 rè dài yǔ lín TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶雨林  
 
tropical fruit n (fruit that grows in equatorial areas)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带水果  
 
tropical island n (isle in the tropics)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带岛屿，热带小岛  
 
tropical medicine n (study of diseases of the tropics)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带病医学 rè dài bìng yī xué  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带病学 rè dài bìng yī xué，rè dài bìng xué 
 -- Tropical medicine deals with diseases that are rarely seen in the US.
 
tropical paradise n (idyllic location in equatorial area)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带天堂，热带乐园  
 
tropical rainforest, tropical rain forest n (dense woodland in equatorial area)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带雨林 rè dài yǔ lín TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶雨林  
 
tropical storm n (cyclone)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带气旋 rè dài qì xuán TC Traditional Chinese 熱帶氣旋  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 热带风暴 rè dài qì xuán，rè dài fēng bào 
 -- The tropical storm caused major flooding and wind damage.

在这些条目还发现' tropical '：
在英文解释里：
angelfish - bird of paradise - booby - cachou - coati - cycad - dengue - feijoa - ficus - flamboyance - guava - jackfruit - jungle - jungle fever - liana - mango - nontropical - orchid - palm leaves - palm tree - papaw - papaya - parrotfish - persimmon - philodendron - ramie - selva - snailflower - stonefish - subtropical - taro - toucan - tropic - tropical aquarium - tropical fish - yaws
中文：
热带 - 热带鱼

